headline: American Eagle Beats on Q3 Earnings, Stock Falls on Weak Holiday View
summary: AEO's Q3 results reflect gains from strong back-to-school sales and robust comps. However, a weak holiday season forecast and slashed fiscal 2024 view hurt investors' sentiment.
